{"tid":1033744,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【新盤銷情】深水埗AVA228 暫沽46伙","createTime":"2019-02-23T11:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T16:56:00.000Z","uid":10101,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f227227ec38a13b5c3a48a6152d7031702a277a4","tid":1033744,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:50:24.000Z","msg":"由資深投資者盧華家族持有的深水埗AVA228，今日首輪開售82伙。據現場消息透露，截至晚上9時許，暫時有46個單位獲買家揀選，主要以開放式單位最搶手。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，AVA228 昨晚截票，截收264票登記。而發展商是次共推出82伙供買家揀選，最平入場費折實價280.3萬元，屬近兩年來市區最細銀碼的項目。"},{"pid":"0e98750a67f61a070eb015226b4bb3330cb09a1c","tid":1033744,"uid":221051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"冇宣布加推？"},{"pid":"fcce2360fbe1d84864abb0568804fe7359791af5","tid":1033744,"uid":44783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e98750a67f61a070eb015226b4bb3330cb09a1c","tid":1033744,"uid":221051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"冇宣布加推？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:53:33.000Z","msg":"賣得哂都偷笑"},{"pid":"6b02ee4a0129512afc8e6731c5b78c14d06f653c","tid":1033744,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"又話冇人買既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e673c28e976e1a6bb434b331bd3fd434e9dac50b","tid":1033744,"uid":86246,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"個名咁似d番號"},{"pid":"682511b39b228f191b0b993c9ed51d43560d4681","tid":1033744,"uid":195334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"其他市區可能真係清晒 but 深水埗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb144153350d7b0a041ac2f05a38a48c541d2b2","tid":1033744,"uid":10101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"682511b39b228f191b0b993c9ed51d43560d4681","tid":1033744,"uid":195334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24